description: Promote effective testing practices for Java projects.
globs: ["src/test/**/*.java"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- Write clear, concise, and focused unit tests for individual components.
- Use mocking frameworks like Mockito for isolating dependencies in unit tests.
- Implement integration tests to verify interactions between components and external systems.
- Consider using Testcontainers for integration testing with real databases or services.
- Ensure adequate test coverage for critical business logic.